Release v0.1.0 - Boot strap kernel for target system C64 
    - Initial build system - kernel build only
    - Initialize C64 devices
    - Simple console input/output
    - Kernel task captures keyboard input and puts it to the screen
    - Multi source interrupt handler - handles only CIA Timer A   

Release v0.2.0 - Kernel multitasking support, C64 applications and libraries
    - Added kernel multitasking and preemptive scheduler
    - Added example rom for C64, replaces BASIC ROM
    - Added support for C Applications
    - C Library with basic functions for C64 applications
    - Kernel mutex subsystem with libc syscall for C applications
    - Updated build system to build libraries and applications
    - Autogeneration of C and ASM header files for direct calls into kernel
     

